    "body": "`zmq` seems to be an alias for `pyzmq`, and the project page, https://pypi.org/project/zmq/, states \"You are probably looking for pyzmq.\". So switch to `pyzmq`, which is what we document, and use in all other jobs.\r\n\r\nAlso add `pyzmq` to native MSAN, so that `interface_zmq.py` is run.",
